  homepage http://fuse.sourceforge.net/sshfs.html
      desc 'ssh-fuse is a filesystem that uses SFTP.
It is based on Filesystem in Userspace (FUSE), and hence root
privilege is not required for mounting a remote filesystem.
No setup is necessary and it is very easy to use.'
